front.title: •Honor Of The Jedi
front.gametext: Deploy on table. Unless opponent occupies three battlegrounds, each time you must lose Force (except from your card, battle damage or a Force drain at a battleground), reduce the loss by 2. (Immune to Alter while you occupy any battleground).
front.lore: The final act of Luke's ascension to Jedi Knighthood was sending off his father, draped in the garb of Vader.
